{"SEMIBARBARIAN":[{"def":"Half barbarous; partially civilized.","pos":""},{"def":"One partly civilized.","pos":""}],"SEMIBARBARIC":[{"def":"Half barbarous or uncivilized; as, semibarbaric display.","pos":""}],"SEMIBARBARISM":[{"def":"The quality or state of being half barbarous or uncivilized.","pos":""}],"SEMIBREVE":[{"def":"A note of half the time or duration of the breve; -- now usually called a whole note.","pos":""}],"SEMIBULL":[{"def":"A bull issued by a pope in the period between his election and coronation.","pos":""}]}